dc_title_s: Geological map of Bacau, Dili, and Kupang-Atambua quadrangles of Timor
dc_description_s: United Nations. Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific (ESCAP) Companion text: Geology and mineral resources of Timor-Leste. [Bangkok, Thailand] : United Nations. Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific. Atlas of mineral resources of the ESCAP region. 2003. vol. 17. 143p. Relief shown by spot heights. Depth shown by 10 m. contour interval. Universal transverse Mercator (UYM) grid Zone 51L. "Note: Compiled by the Economic and Social Comission for Asia and the Pacific (ESCAP) as supplementary and reference data for the ESCAP Mineral Atlas volume 17: Geology and Mineral Resources of Timor - Leste.".
